# Service registry service

Owns registration, scopes, trust rules, credentials, `/auth/token`, and JWKS.

- Prefer `bin/seed-user-service-s2s.php` for user-service caller packs.
- On `--rotate-credentials`, deactivate previous active hashes before inserting the new secret.
- Consumer wiring docs live under each app's `docs/service-registry.md` (index in `docs/README.md`).
- Never log plaintext shared secrets outside seed stdout.
